=> Scheduler Optimization

1. Objective:

Maximize scheduling efficiency while respecting:
i) User preferences
ii) Duration constraints
iii) Work hours
iv) Conflict avoidance


2. Slot Generation:

Working hours:
09:30 – 18:30
Algorithm:
i) Sort busy intervals
ii) Identify gaps
iii) Validate duration


3. Ranking Algorithm:

Score components:
PreferenceScore:
+10 if matches preferred time window
ConflictPenalty:
i) High penalty if overlap
FragmentationPenalty:
ii) Penalize short fragmented slots


4. Optimization Formula:

Score = PreferenceWeight 
        i) ConflictPenalty
        ii) TimeFragmentationCost


5. Example:

User prefers mornings.
Available slots:
09:30–10:30
14:00–15:00
Morning slot gets higher score.
